name: Norris
content:
Norris was a Human male smuggler who operated out of the city of Nashal on the Twin World of Talus during the time of the Galactic Civil War.
Norris was a non-player character in the 2003 video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. Norris was added to the game along with the smuggling missions introduced with the "Chapter 3" update, released on September 27, 2006.
